<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="container py-5">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-lg-8">
      <div class="profile-card p-4 p-md-5">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="mv-icon-wrap m-0">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h1 class="fw-bold mb-0" style="font-size: 2rem; color: var(--nm-text);">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-muted mb-0" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Last updated: July 2026</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="lead text-muted mb-4" style="font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.75;">
          At Neuro_Mentor, we take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our peer-to-peer mentorship platform.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-4" style="border-color: var(--nm-border-light);">

        <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-4">
          <div>
            <h4 class="fw-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--nm-text); font-size: 1.25rem;">1. Information We Collect</h4>
            <p class="text-muted" style="line-height: 1.7;">
              We collect information you provide directly to us when you create an account, complete your student profile, register as an educator, or communicate with us. This includes your name, email, academic/professional background, and uploaded credentials.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h4 class="fw-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--nm-text); font-size: 1.25rem;">2. How We Use Your Information</h4>
            <ul class="text-muted ps-3 d-flex flex-column gap-2" style="line-height: 1.7;">
              <li>To connect students with matching educators based on subject interests.</li>
              <li>To process bookings and maintain your platform wallet balances.</li>
              <li>To verify the credentials and identities of registered educators for platform safety.</li>
              <li>To improve our website functionality, resolve support problems, and prevent fraud.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h4 class="fw-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--nm-text); font-size: 1.25rem;">3. Data Security & Storage</h4>
            <p class="text-muted" style="line-height: 1.7;">
              Your data is stored securely using industry-standard database encryptions. Profile images and identity proofs are hosted safely via Cloudinary. We never sell your personal information to third parties.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h4 class="fw-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--nm-text); font-size: 1.25rem;">4. Your Choices & Rights</h4>
            <p class="text-muted" style="line-height: 1.7;">
              You have the right to view, edit, or delete your student profile or educator listing at any time. If you wish to delete your account entirely, please reach out to us through our Contact Form.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-5 text-center">
          <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary rounded-pill px-4">Back to Home</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
